<concept id="concept_3413BBD173324104B42FB714974CABE7" xml:lang="en-us">
    <title>Defining Marketable Services</title>
    <conbody>
        <section>
            <p>The general procedure for defining a marketable service in <ph
                    conref="../../Shared/Product_Name.xml#ProductNameTopic/Product_Abbr"/> is the following: </p>
            <ol>
                <li>Create the marketable service.<ph audience="doc"> For details, refer to <xref
                        href="../MarketableServices/c_MSCreate.xml"/>.</ph></li>
                <li>Define a price model for the service.<ph audience="doc"> For details, refer to <xref
                        href="../PriceModels/c_PMIntro.xml"/>.</ph></li>
                <li>Define upgrade and downgrade options (optional).<ph audience="doc"> For details, refer to <xref
                        href="../MarketableServices/c_MSUpgrade.xml"/>.</ph></li>
            </ol>
        </section>
    </conbody>
</concept>
